data.description: How does 0% down sound?? This home qualifies for USDA financing! Beautiful 3-bedroom two bath home nestled in the sought-after Canyon Creek lakeside community. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the spaciousness of the living, dining, and kitchen areas that boast 9-foot ceilings and lots of windows. The open floor plan creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining friends or family time. Enjoy the giant kitchen island with waterfall countertop, giant drawers for pots and pans, soft close drawers and breakfast bar. Kitchen also features a window above the sink, sink with no touch sensor faucet, pull out trash cabinet and built in microwave. The primary bedroom is near the living room and boasts a giant walk-in closet. This home features a split floorplan ideal for children, guests, or an office. This subdivision offers the security of a guarded gate, a community dock, boat ramp, community pool, tennis courts, close to downtown, playgrounds and more.
